Global Smart Parking Payment Machine Market Insights
Smart Parking Payment Machine Market size was valued at USD 2.57 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 6.12 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Smart Parking Payment Machine Market Overview
The global Smart Parking Payment Machine market size is expected to reach USD 2.1 billion by 2027, growing at a CAGR of 14.6% during the forecast period. The increasing demand for automated parking systems, rising urbanization, and advancements in IoT technology are major factors driving market growth. As cities evolve towards smart infrastructure, integrating digital payment solutions for parking is becoming a necessity for enhancing the user experience. With the ongoing push towards sustainability and improved traffic management, the Smart Parking Payment Machine market is poised for substantial growth across key regions.

