7. How does smart parking improve sustainability?
By reducing the time spent searching for parking, it lowers emissions and contributes to environmental sustainability.

8. What are the key drivers for the adoption of smart parking payment systems?
Convenience, contactless payments, and better traffic management are key factors driving adoption.

9. What impact has COVID-19 had on the Smart Parking Payment Machine market?
The pandemic accelerated the shift towards contactless and automated parking solutions to minimize physical interactions.

10. How can small municipalities afford smart parking systems?
With the rise of scalable and cost-effective solutions, even smaller municipalities can adopt smart parking technologies.

